DataElement.preferredName: OME TIFF Big Endian Byte Order True False Indicator
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A response of true or false to indicate if the Open Microscopy Environment (OME) tagged image file format (TIFF) image file consisted of multiple bytes in which the most significant bit is encoded first with the remaining bytes encoded in decreasing order of significance.

DataElementConcept.preferredName: OME Tagged Image File Format Big Endian Byte Order
DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: A tagged image file format (TIFF) image file format that contains an Open Microscopy Environment (OME) XML metadata block in the file header for storing microscopy information (pixels and metadata) using the OME Data Model._A binary number consisting of multiple bytes in which the most significant bit is encoded first with the remaining bytes encoded in decreasing order of significance.
